.IX Item "characters"
Receive notification of character data.
.Sp
.Vb 1
\& Data             The characters from the XML document.
.Ve
.IP "ignorable_whitespace" 4
.IX Item "ignorable_whitespace"
Receive notification of ignorable whitespace in element content.
.Sp
.Vb 1
\& Data             The characters from the XML document.
.Ve
